title: T205-era Honest Long Cut Tobacco Pack (Empty)
author: canjond

posts.post_title: T205-era Honest Long Cut Tobacco Pack (Empty)
posts.post_content:
Up for sale is an extra T205-era Honest Long Cut tobacco wrapper.  The wrapper is in fair condition overall, with some flaking, but strong visual graphics.  The wrapper has also been "stuffed" with foam to give the appearance of full (the top foil still folds down without issue).  Remnants of the tax stamp on the sides is still present.

$45.00 shipped.
